item.title: Google Data Analytics Capstone: Cyclistic Bike Share
item.description: Preface: I’ll be presenting my data analysis to a big audience. Several people present are, Lily Moreno: the director of marketing and my manager over at a fictious company named, Cyclistic including the marketing analystics team and the executive team. For detail context of the capstone case study including steps of the data preparations, please follow this Github link. Background: “How do annual members and casual riders use Cyclistic bikes differently?
